{"tid":532729,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李國章缺席馬斐森師生大型歡送會","createTime":"2018-01-18T06:23:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-18T06:48:52.000Z","uid":28195,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3a53bf53b42a0833d506fbb76175f470ea94866d","tid":532729,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T06:23:13.000Z","msg":"馬斐森月底卸任　師生搞大型歡送會　李國章缺席<br />\n<br />\n港大校長馬斐森將於月底卸任，港大師生及校友今午在陸佑堂為其舉行歡送會，有數百人出席，包括首席副校長譚廣亨、校委會前主席梁智鴻、醫學院院長梁卓偉等，惟校董會主席李國章則缺席。馬斐森在聚會上指，過去四年的生活過得非常特別，對學生感到自豪，又希望港大未來仍視他為朋友。<br />\n<br />\n對於繼任者張翔，馬斐森回應稱，希望外界給他一個機會，並祝願對方一切順利。<br />\n<br />\n馬斐森今午攜同妻子出席歡送會並致辭，陸佑堂舞台上，則寫有「多謝和歡送馬斐森」的字句。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E9%A6%AC%E6%96%90%E6%A3%AE%E6%9C%88%E5%BA%95%E5%8D%B8%E4%BB%BB-%E5%B8%AB%E7%94%9F%E6%90%9E%E5%A4%A7%E5%9E%8B%E6%AD%A1%E9%80%81%E6%9C%83-%E6%9D%8E%E5%9C%8B%E7%AB%A0%E7%BC%BA%E5%B8%AD/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E6%2596%2590%25E6%25A3%25AE%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%25BA%2595%25E5%258D%25B8%25E4%25BB%25BB-%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%2590%259E%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%259E%258B%25E6%25AD%25A1%25E9%2580%2581%25E6%259C%2583-%25E6%259D%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%25AB%25A0%25E7%25BC%25BA%25E5%25B8%25AD%2F&d=K57mQQZxUvxwTeepu0IeDJzN29kXmk9bB7xBuKM86BA%3D&h=2d850900\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E6%2596%2590%25E6%25A3%25AE%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%25BA%2595%25E5%258D%25B8%25E4%25BB%25BB-%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%2590%259E%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%259E%258B%25E6%25AD%25A1%25E9%2580%2581%25E6%259C%2583-%25E6%259D%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%25AB%25A0%25E7%25BC%25BA%25E5%25B8%25AD%2F&h=f7d4bc86\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E9%A6%AC%E6%96%90%E6%A3%AE%E6%9C%88%E5%BA%95%E5%8D%B8%E4%BB%BB-%E5%B8%AB%E7%94%9F%E6%90%9E%E5%A4%A7%E5%9E%8B%E6%AD%A1%E9%80%81%E6%9C%83-%E6%9D%8E%E5%9C%8B%E7%AB%A0%E7%BC%BA%E5%B8%